com.genband.kandy.api.services.calls

Class GSMCallPhoneStateListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.telephony.PhoneStateListener
      • com.genband.kandy.api.services.calls.GSMCallPhoneStateListener

  • public class GSMCallPhoneStateListener
extends PhoneStateListener
    Listener which listen to phone state changes ( PhoneStateListener.LISTEN_CALL_STATE) and used for handling of the GSM call callbacks KandyGSMCallServiceNotificationListener.onGSMCallIncoming(IKandyCall, String) , KandyGSMCallServiceNotificationListener.onGSMCallConnected(IKandyCall, String) and KandyGSMCallServiceNotificationListener.onGSMCallDisconnected(IKandyCall, String)

    Logic:
    • TelephonyManager.CALL_STATE_RINGING -> onGSMCallIncoming isRinging := true
    • TelephonyManager.CALL_STATE_OFFHOOK -> if(isRingning) then onGSMCallConnected and isCallInProcess := true
    • TelephonyManager.CALL_STATE_IDLE -> No Active Calls if(isRinging) then incoming call rejected if(isCallInProcess) then onGSMCallDisconnected isCallInProcess := false
